description: Serves meat, veg options available. Child-friendly cafe next to the Senate Square. Lunch menu has occasional vegan choice, and kitchen will make you a sandwich if there is no vegan option ready. Be sure to mention if vegan so staff will know to fix you extras if there is something missing for vegans. Sometimes will bake a vegan chocolate cake. At breakfast there is porridge with soy milk. Keeps soy milk and oat milk for coffee.
